Class RESTWebServiceUtils

    • com.anthem.selenium.utils.RESTWebServiceUtils
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MimeConstants, WebServiceConstants

    public class RESTWebServiceUtils
extends Object
implements WebServiceConstants
     This class provides the methods for Consuming and querying REST Webservices.
 Check WebServiceConstants for supported Constants.
 All methods without the requestType parameter defaults to GET request.
 All methods without loggingRequired (boolean) parameter has default Extent Reports Logging enabled.
 All methods with ..._Headers corresponds to accessing webservice with only Headers.
 
 For Authentication Purpose, Please pass credentials in header/headerMap.
 eg:- Map headerMap = new HashMap();
        
 For Using Basic Authentication
                String credentials = "AF99999" + ":" + "TestPwd";
                byte[] encodedBytes = Base64.getEncoder().encode(credentials.getBytes());
                String encoding = new String(encodedBytes);
                headerMap.put("Authorization", String.format("Basic %s", encoding));
 
 For Using OAuth Authentication (pass accessToken value)
                headerMap.put("Authorization", "Bearer " + accessToken);
 
 For Authentication purpose use *_Headers() methods.
